text: The 1956 Navy Midshipmen football team represented the United States Naval Academy (USNA) during the 1956 NCAA University Division football season. Navy competed as an independent with no conference affiliation. The team was led by seventh-year head coach Eddie Erdelatz. ==Schedule== ==References== |Navy Midshipmen Category:Navy Midshipmen football seasons Navy Midship
